  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t微博头号包粉“王虎的舰桥”在包帝服软防疫减速之后气急败坏，先是昨天发了一篇暗示希望胡锦涛早死的微博，结果被平台封禁一个月，今天转战他的小号“吴知山”继续发帖，暗示动态清零的被迫中止是李克强使的阴谋诡计，包帝被蒙在鼓里。然后这几条微博下面大量的包粉开始集体听床，希望立刻清算李克强和胡锡进等反包势力。链接：https://weibo.com/u/7327928667，可以看他最近几条微博下的回复，我只截图了一小部分，大量包粉在怒骂\"莉卡酱\"<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvOWJlZjQ0MmVlNWFjNGJlOGY2NDEzLnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/9bef442ee5ac4be8f6413.png\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/9bef442ee5ac4be8f6413.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/9bef442ee5ac4be8f6413.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvMWIwYzM1YjYzNGFjOWU1YzU3ZDVjLnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/1b0c35b634ac9e5c57d5c.png\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/1b0c35b634ac9e5c57d5c.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/1b0c35b634ac9e5c57d5c.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvYWY2ZDI2YmQwNzhiNDhmZmI0ZjJlLnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/af6d26bd078b48ffb4f2e.png\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/af6d26bd078b48ffb4f2e.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/af6d26bd078b48ffb4f2e.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a> </div>",
